	<div id="intro" style="float: center;">
		<p>In the past few decades, job loss due to automation has spiked dramatically as machine efficiency increases further and further. This has led to a large disenfranchised population, and many people are worried they won't be able to find work due to the cost of education needed to seek out new jobs. Here at the Community Forge, our goal is to give these people hope by providing educational resources allowing them to learn skills allowing them to make hand crafted goods and perform various other tasks that are, and most likely will continue to be, difficult to automate.
<br>
<br>
This IPRO was heavily inspired by the Community Tool Box which you can learn more about by clicking <a href="https://ctb.ku.edu/en">here</a> 
</p>
